description: A Trucker Jacket makes an outfit. You'd be hard-pressed to find a jacket with an easier shape, more versatile weight or inherent sense of cool. Bonus: The deep inside pockets are roomy enough for your essentials.

name: EUCLID ANORAK JACKET
description: The '90s are back and we're so here for it. Brought to life in a washed pastel lavender, this jacket channels the best of the decade.

name: ORIGINAL FIT MAN'S JEANS
description: Close your eyes. Think “jeans.” Now open. They were 501s®, right? With a classic straight leg and iconic styling, they’re literally the blueprint for every pair of jeans in existence — burned into the world’s collective cortex ever since Levi Strauss (the man himself!) invented them in 1873. To this day they've never gone out of style. And they never will.

name: FLES JEANS
description: A worn-in, ’90s-inspired take on our Original Trucker Jacket. Levi’s® iconic, instantly recognizable jean jacket has been a symbol of individual self-expression for decades. With a boxy silhouette, this Vintage Fit Trucker Jacket is built with more room in the shoulder and sleeves.

name: TRUCKER JACKET
description: Levi’s® 502™ Regular Taper Jeans are a more refined, modern alternative to the straight jean you love. Extra room in the thigh and a clean, tapered cut make them easy to style without compromising comfort.

name: FLEX MEN'S JEANS
description: The are two secrets to a good hoodie: comfort and versatility. With soft French terry and an easy-to-style, relaxed fit, this one's got both.

name: SUNSET TRUCKER JACKET
description: With a vintage fit, supersoft French terry and a unisex design, these joggers have everything you want in sweats, and none of the stuff you don’t. Your other clothes will miss you.

name: SLIM TAPOR
description: Our beloved Vintage Fit Trucker Jacket—brought to life with a patchworrk design. Future you will thank you.n

name: FADON DENIM SHIRT
description: No summer line-up's complete without a camp shirt (or three). It breathes the relaxed vibe that summer's all about, but is slightly more stepped-up than a T-shirt.

name: TRUCKER JACKET
description: Trucker Jacket is our cool borrowed-from-the-boys take on the original Trucker Jacket. With a more oversized silhouette, it's perfect for layering over sweaters and hoodies.

name: 90's TRUCKER JACKET
description: A Trucker Jacket makes an outfit. You'd be hard-pressed to find a jacket with an easier shape, more versatile weight or inherent sense of cool. Bonus: This throwback cut features a pitched silhouette for a distinctly ‘90s feel.

name: CHERYAL MITCHELL
description: A chore coat unlike any other. We took this classic style and gave it a mini update with a non-traditional shrunken construction. And because a jacket is only as good as its pockets, we gave this one plenty—so you can leave the bag at home.

name: SHRUNKEN CHORE COAT
description: A chore coat unlike any other. We took this classic style and gave it a mini update with a non-traditional shrunken construction. And because a jacket is only as good as its pockets, we gave this one plenty—so you can leave the bag at home.

name: ORANGE TAB JACKET
description: An emblem of the pioneering spirit, the Trucker Jacket is a Levi’s® original that’s made history. Our iconic, instantly recognizable jean jacket has been a symbol of individual self-expression for decades. It’s also a perfect in-between layer that looks just as good over a tee or under a coat.

name: SLIM RIB T-SHIRT
description: A Trucker Jacket makes an outfit. You'd be hard-pressed to find a jacket with an easier shape, more versatile weight or inherent sense of cool. This relaxed cut features an elongated front hem and a cozy, pajama-like fit.

name: ORIGINAL SHERPA TRUCKER JACKET
description: A classic with a twist, our Sherpa Trucker is a cozy take on our original Trucker Jacket that’s built with a fuzzy sherpa lining for extra warmth. This amazingly versatile staple combines the cool and the cozy all while keeping it as authentic as its namesake.

name: CAPOLA PUFF SLEEVE BLOUSE
description: The perfect outfit for an afternoon in the park? This versatile Capola Top and whatever you like on bottom. Pair with sunglasses and a picnic basket for the sweetest look of the season.

name: HYBRID TRUCKER JACKETS
description: A little oversized, a lot of attitude. Designed with an extra-relaxed silhouette, our Levi’s® Ex-Boyfriend Trucker Jacket is an ideal outer layer whose slight drop shoulder creates a cool, borrowed-from-the-boys look. This unique hybrid model features comfy cloth sleeves and a frayed bottom hem

name: RIBCAGE DENIM SKIRT
description: Our highest high rise, reimagined as a versatile denim skirt. It's become a hip-slimming and waist-defining obsession

name: 10' MEN'S SHORTS
description: Good denim shorts need no fuss or frills. That's why we kept it simple and designed these with just this basics: quality denim, classic 5-pocket styling and a versatile fit that hits just above the knees.

name: PANHANDLE JACKET
description: Grandpa fishing vibes—and we mean that in the best of ways. Constructed with sturdy ripstop, roomy snap pockets and a contrast collar, this jacket will do the trick whether you're camping, glamping or exploring the city.

name: STOCK TRUCKER JACKET
description: Some styles transcend time and trend, and somehow manage to get better with age. A denim jacket is without a doubt one of them. We made this one with a boxy fit and distinct pockets

name: RELAXED FIT WESTERN SHIRT
description: Our iconic Western Shirt—reimagined with a contemporary relaxed fit. With durable denim and timeless style, this is the kind of piece you'll wear for years and hand down for generations to come

name: 1 POCKET STANDARD FIT SHIRT
description: Casual, but not sloppy. Put-together, but not stuffy. Wear this shirt buttoned to the top for a classic look, or ignore the buttons altogether and wear open, layered over your favorite T-shirt for a more relaxed style. There's no wrong way to wear this timeless staple.
